PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1133 - FLUAZIFOP-BUTYL) which establish maximum limits (MRLs) on residues of the herbicide fluazifop-butyl that can be detected on or in eggs or in the fat and meat of cattle, goats, hogs, horses, poultry and sheep, and in their by-products.
